        class I {

            }

                return !!this.ctrl && this.ctrl.canStart(this.name)
            }
            start() {
                return !!this.ctrl && this.ctrl.start(this.name, this.id, this.priority)
            }
            capture() {

                    return !1;

            }

            }

            constructor(R, T, P, K) {
                this.id = T,
                this.disable = P,
                this.disableScroll = K,
                this.ctrl = R
            }

                    if (this.disable)
                        for (const R of this.disable)
                            this.ctrl.disableGesture(R, this.id);
                    this.disableScroll && this.ctrl.disableScroll(this.id)
                }
            }
            unblock() {
                if (this.ctrl) {
                    if (this.disable)
                        for (const R of this.disable)
                            this.ctrl.enableGesture(R, this.id);
                    this.disableScroll && this.ctrl.enableScroll(this.id)
                }
            }

                this.unblock(),
                this.ctrl = void 0
            }
        }

                        t.present()

                }
                shakeAttempt() {

                        t.state = !1
                    }
                    , 0)

        let AF = (()=>{
            class e {
                constructor(t, r, o) {
                    this.gameService = t,
                    this.toastController = r,
                    this.modalController = o,
                    this.countdown = "",
                    this.stats = null
                }
                ngOnInit() {
                    this.updateCountdown(),
                    this.gameService.afterGameStateChanged().pipe(So(t=>null !== t)).subscribe(()=>{
                        this.updateStats()
                    }
                    ),
                    this.updateStats()
                }
                hasWon() {
                    return this.gameService.hasWon()
                }
                hasLost() {
                    return this.gameService.hasLost()
                }
                copyShare() {
                    this.gameService.copyStateToClipboard(),
                    this.toastController.create({
                        message: "Ergebnis kopiert.",
                        duration: 2e3
                    }).then(t=>{
                        t.present()
                    }
                    )
                }
                updateCountdown() {
                    const t = new Date;
                    let r = "" + (23 - t.getHours())
                      , o = "" + (59 - t.getMinutes())
                      , i = "" + (60 - t.getSeconds());
                    setTimeout(()=>{
                        this.updateCountdown()
                    }
                    , 1e3),
                    1 === r.length && (r = "0" + r),
                    1 === o.length && (o = "0" + o),
                    1 === i.length && (i = "0" + i),
                    this.countdown = `${r}:${o}:${i}`
                }
                getTarget() {
                    var t;
                    return (null === (t = this.gameService.state) || void 0 === t ? void 0 : t.target) || ""
                }
                updateStats() {
                    const t = {
                        total: 0,
                        currentStreak: 0,
                        longestStreak: 0,
                        entries: []
                    };
                    t.total = this.gameService.history.winWithNum.reduce((o,i)=>o + i, 0),
                    t.total += this.gameService.history.numLost,
                    t.currentStreak = this.gameService.history.currentStreak,
                    t.longestStreak = this.gameService.history.longestStreak;
                    const r = this.gameService.history.winWithNum.map(o=>o / t.total).reduce((o,i)=>Math.max(o, i), 0);
                    this.gameService.history.winWithNum.forEach((o,i)=>{
                        t.entries.push({
                            numWins: o,
                            perc: t.total ? Math.round(100 * o / t.total) : 0,
                            relPerc: t.total ? o / t.total / r : 0
                        })
                    }
                    ),
                    this.stats = t
                }
                dismissModal() {
                    this.modalController.dismiss()
                }
                getPercentage() {
                    return this.stats.total ? (this.stats.entries.map(r=>r.numWins).reduce((r,o)=>r + o, 0) / this.stats.total * 100).toFixed(2) + "%" : "--%"
                }
            }

            class e {

                    if (!t.ctrlKey && !t.metaKey) {

                            return void this.triggerRemove();

                            return void this.triggerSend();

                            r.forEach(o=>{
                                o === t.key.toLocaleUpperCase() && this.triggerKey(o)

                        }
                        )
                    }
